org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules WHERE enabled_modules.project_id IN (SELECT projects.id FROM projects WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (7, 12))) AND enabled_modules.name = "$1" LIMIT "$2"

rewrites.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules WHERE enabled_modules.project_id IN (SELECT projects.id FROM projects WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (7, 12) LIMIT 1)) AND enabled_modules.name = "$1" LIMIT "$2"
